  <front>
   <head>Epigrammi - III. In Bubonem.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Nam quis te, inepte Bubo, tam stolidus furor</l>
     <l n="2">Adegit importunum inire praelium,</l>
     <l n="3">Isto indecenti rostro, et alis luridis?</l>
     <l n="4">Quid bellicosae volucris, insulse, asperos</l>
     <l n="5">Lacessis ungues? desine, miser, dum licet;</l>
     <l n="6">Ne dormientis excites somnum tuo</l>
     <l n="7">Cum maximo, ut par est, malo, ac clade ultima.</l>
     <l n="8">Sed pervenire vis in ora vulgi; et hac</l>
     <l n="9">Via cupis, sceleste, fieri notior?</l>
     <l n="10">Non assequere; nec profecto tam bono</l>
     <l n="11">Fruere fato. An hoc pudendo sanguine</l>
     <l n="12">Se tingat Aquila, fulminum et caeli immemor?</l>
     <l n="13">Ponenda honestae mortis haec spes est tibi.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
